- [ ] All components in the module have at least one scenario
- [ ] All form fields have validation scenarios
- [ ] All HTTP endpoints are covered (happy + error paths)
- [ ] Auth-guarded routes are tested
- [ ] All helpers are in place with JSDoc comments
- [ ] Tests pass in CI (chromium + firefox)
- [ ] PR is raised with results table and screenshots attached
- [ ] Feature file has user-editable comment markers

